## Site Configuration
Contains reusable content blocks found throughout the site which contain specific layout renderings, and content from Sitecore Field Sections and Templates. Dynamic renderings are one portion of what is available and are predefined layouts that allow content editors to craft custom content within those layouts, which are commonly referred to as Frames, Framesets, or Frameset Groups(see below)
